{"id":"87df6e193d5835da4cc2c9df10256b2eaa8067333f61c7d48671630702a2eb78","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:0","text":"与所有纹理类节点一样，此节点接受一个 manifold，用于通过 UVs 执行 2D 放置，或通过 3D 投影应用分形纹理。默认行为是：如果没有连接 manifold，就在 3D 中基于 P 进行应用。"}
{"id":"d1e3d635bf4084423df941ecf74cd1709a4efa9811a050cc191885400fe4a027","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:2","text":"Surface Position"}
{"id":"0cd4048b786093a9ee031641b4e38b38fdf142d5b04de850bf325ba993abab30","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:3","text":"噪声可以基于"}
{"id":"709fe7f143bc3c1afe3c9f14565b798314f47dd342a7730df546f478ceb3e5f3","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:4","text":"Current Position"}
{"id":"ba4b7cfc09d78634ff53cd009a1e4c2507b4743429b2e538e2e01c8acee00138","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:5","text":"或"}
{"id":"579996376b0f5f3926642832076464a78dafd8c8328e5625ecc07a19e114e8b8","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:9","text":"Undisplaced Position"}
{"id":"4ff23c279f8ca82275babe7ce7963f83c4d33ee35bde9dacb74fd6b7097a8e47","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:7","text":"（位移之前的表面位置）计算。"}
{"id":"c848ab50f5f05803ec189c1929892f987d0768d454c500b94447949883cf3983","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:8","text":"如果希望置换图案和着色图案匹配，请使用"}
{"id":"0bcd66e677f4ee7288547da02b6cd5594fd8b8c3abbc6482dfd42c788ecbe448","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:11","text":"Layers"}
{"id":"9b718bd7626ebfca9b45d0f1740a7c3afb11d8594aa53b36ed8697c491a031cb","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:12","text":"使用的噪声层数量。更多层会逐层添加更多噪声，产生更细致的图案。"}
{"id":"16b6668d9831a1b8d2d003496db6a62b7f525df6c556d7c04681fbed2251c845","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:13","text":"Frequency"}
{"id":"3136e9746a5b5564406a626b34cdd1960e06b4b56ae75801db68869da883ceed","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:14","text":"设置噪声层的最低（起始）频率。"}
{"id":"398e224a07132498c549dd0bac93a2594886c0dd15b062b3ce501c4e5c01eae3","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:15","text":"Lacunarity"}
{"id":"059dc246674a04f74479067834c9c118d37dba6e30565172695f779394a16bdc","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:16","text":"用于确定每个后续噪声层频率的尺度。较小数值会使各层在频率上更接近；较大数值会使它们相距更远。"}
{"id":"0bc70684cf306b3ed9ab68fd40654349b8fdf96b2e6cdce61edc53442d7f738f","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:17","text":"Dimension"}
{"id":"d4e1aa848b8a2817e6b34ea9799357f8d5fa2705f2f88a40a45b91f3e655f61c","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:18","text":"频率指数。此值会使用公式 1/f^(3-2*Dimension) 缩放每个后续噪声层的幅度；其中 f 是给定层所用噪声的频率。它称为 dimension，因为该值与分形维度相关。数值越大越粗糙，数值越小越平滑。"}
{"id":"d41111129d818b2e53798dfe5c54057645aec02c94bec863cf95062942eb8132","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:19","text":"Erosion"}
{"id":"0f35b52f0c3d1138c8f141ebfce9bd2bb67a87a342ded229d02d5881ee015034","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:20","text":"频率指数范围。负值会平滑低值区域，正值会平滑高值区域。由 dimension 指定的频率指数本身会按噪声幅度发生偏移；此值用于调整该偏移。这决定了所谓的分形交叉尺度。0 会产生 uniform（均匀）外观。"}
{"id":"8dc605f468e5eca3e2f7ac6ad049c18c2eccd08e22acddfcb86933fa8456276c","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:21","text":"Variation"}
{"id":"100297ec445fedeac1f963456eecad2e806d69feb79b52e145d63ec81ff6471b","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:22","text":"此值控制获得哪一种外观变化，而不会改变由其他控制项决定的外观属性。因此，例如可以通过连接到 Time 来为外观制作动画，或通过设置不同数值来创建多个独特的外观实例。"}
{"id":"5e23ec6a300dc60a79641769017e16e9bf042cbd8fd0a54586a048ab9da972ff","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:23","text":"Mode"}
{"id":"d99980e83c29dd7acd9cb9977260092c111b3cfac057954dc631ab144b3bc9c5","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:24","text":"对噪声倍频程执行 modeOp 的不同方式"}
{"id":"51e588e2344b4d7c9052d3587e2c2aa234f7122cd9858e8f2576cb16596920a1","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:26","text":"应用噪声所使用的 manifold。默认为 P。"}
{"id":"ba71a7c085ac16c7de307e2e5aa8c79dbf1bdf5a8f5c762508150f6f2ca94568","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:27","text":"Adjust Output"}
{"id":"1aa6cfeeea19be4fbc48af4632be06cabff3dbbdf85d83a7b4d87a7cbff4130f","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:28","text":"Color Scale"}
{"id":"357de7170a2a222705b18022e71d03f3ccfaa3e29f07d77afef37049ca7c6318","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:29","text":"用于纹理颜色值的乘数，可用来调整亮度或操控单个颜色通道"}
{"id":"c54f3e0aa08775c55e47d2cf166b9abf18efa1edd69d16a07effb5ef590201d4","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:30","text":"Color Offset"}
{"id":"53974a1945e8609215f7432f457ea84d46c68c98bfe25df5e3a212b92cef82f0","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:31","text":"对结果应用偏移，从而移动结果的颜色"}
{"id":"46cf5c71d429968d1d70ed3bdf7df7658dde598a7f93d698f3fe8fb55890ec46","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:32","text":"Float Scale"}
{"id":"7982a153d87a4ccbd6ce94c5a2d4583aff7f5d9e6f08caaa30502c6d63c531e2","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:33","text":"用于 alpha channel 的数值乘数；在用该通道驱动参数时很有用"}
{"id":"3c4a9da2ced3ea1f9286121722248c6a3d226a131039d9d546f0468a55acc769","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:34","text":"Float Offset"}
{"id":"eb2303cc667b45e669cb8f31dac12df6b4a3741a9f0800608da69bbed4b25259","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:35","text":"用于 alpha channel 的偏移；在用该通道驱动参数时很有用"}
{"id":"20cee54d3870761a41a354946a213694c0612e819dc7d1e21f529a8e727fb539","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:37","text":"resultF"}
{"id":"a116c978f7b4c79a57d43cbb86ca52debe423a552f1139a54b214cec49fdfef0","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:38","text":"分形纹理作为 float 时的结果。"}
{"id":"250a5d421d8d242d3132e058c5031a2d7054ea3bbfc6702ccdcfd8751292b390","item_id":"14c65a1eb6:40","text":"作为颜色的分形纹理。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "14c65a1eb6:1", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "14c65a1eb6:10", "text": "。"}
{"id": "e29793dea8429f58cc913ce697117a3614eaa231b5a3942af954b66c44d43850", "item_id": "14c65a1eb6:25", "text": "Manifold"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "14c65a1eb6:36", "text": "Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "14c65a1eb6:39", "text": "resultRGB"}
